What Was Deferred\n\n**Optional configuration files** (not blocking workflow execution):\n\n| File | Purpose | Status |\n|------|---------|--------|\n| `.golangci.yml` | golangci-lint configuration | ⚠️ Not created (optional) |\n| `pyproject.toml` | Ruff/codespell configuration | ⚠️ Not created (optional) |\n| `manifest.yaml` | Dify plugin metadata | ⚠️ Not created (only needed when publishing plugin) |\n\n**Secrets requiring manual configuration:**\n- `CODECOV_TOKEN` - for coverage uploads (workflow works without it)\n- `PLUGIN_ACTION` - for Dify plugin publishing (only needed for plugin feature)\n- `PYPI_API_TOKEN` - for Python SDK/CLI publishing (future use)\n\n**Original proposal scope changes:**\nThe initial proposal (proposal.md) described 13 different workflows including `ci.yml`, `cd.yml`, `security-scan.yml`, `docs.yml`, `multi-arch-build.yml`, `nightly-build.yml`, `pr-validation.yml`, `release.yml`, `dependency-review.yml`, `stale.yml`, `labeler.yml` plus `dependabot.yml`, `labeler.yml` (rules), and `CODEOWNERS`. \n\nThe implemented scope (tasks.md) focused on **12 core workflows** aligned with actual project needs:\n- Deferred: `security-scan.yml` (Trivy/CodeQL), `docs.yml`, `multi-arch-build.yml`, `nightly-build.yml`, `pr-validation.yml`, `release.yml`, `dependency-review.yml`, `stale.yml`, `labeler.yml` (workflow), `dependabot.yml`, `CODEOWNERS`\n- These can be added in future ARs as needed\n\n---\n\n**Status:** ✅ COMPLETE - All 12 specified workflows implemented and verified. No blocking issues.","time":{"start":1775884314886,"end":1775884314886}}}
